+-[Delay's delay's delay's...]----------------------------------------------+

After much delays and stuff like that, we finally released The Ascii Gallery.
It started out as a little project, with only a few ascii's and musics,
but later we decided to add a cuty-style intro, and a hidden part.
Mayby we even started a new style of ascii collections!
But remember, copyright 1996 EFFECT! :)

+-[System requirements.]----------------------------------------------------+

This demo runs on any Amiga with 1 megabyte of chipmemory, and 
1 megabyte of other memory.
things may be a tad slow sometimes on a standart 68000, but runs perfectly
on a 68020 or higher.

