+-[Installing The Ascii Gallery to HD.]-------------------------------------+

Create a new drawer on your harddisk.
copy the following files to that directory:

Ascii_Gallery.Exe
Ascii_Gallery.Doc

And also copy the entire Data drawer over to the directory on your HD.

To make the demo run from your HD, you need to assign the name
Ascii_Gallery: to the drawer on your HD.

You can also use the scriptfile in the HD drawer of the original disk.

Now type Ascii_gallery.Exe to run the demo.
(or the special script file ofcourse :))

